text: Abdesselem Lahmidi (born 1926) is a Moroccan former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1926 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Moroccan male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Morocco Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rabat
